Top Stories (February 27)

CALIFORNIA LIFTS POWER ALERTS, BUT EXPERTS SAY CRISIS IS FAR FROM RESOLVED
As oddly as it arrived, California's electric emergency lifted Thursday 
morning. At 9 a.m., the Independent System Operator, which controls most of 
California's grid, ended a Stage 1 alert. It was the first time since Jan. 13 
that the state hadn't been under a power emergency, declared when low 
supplies threaten grid stability.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMAKRT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/knightri
dder/2001/02/27/krtbn/0000-0338-SA-POWER-ALERT

PACIFIC GAS & ELECTRIC DECLINES COMMENT ON STATUS OF POWER GRID SALE TALKS
PG&E Corp. declined to confirm California Gov. Gray Davis' prediction Tuesday 
that the state will conclude an agreement to buy the transmission assets of 
its Pacific Gas & Electric Co. utility unit within two or three weeks.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
02/27/eng-djn/eng-djn_210053_90_2343033626676

US HIGH COURT SAYS EPA ERRED IN SETTING OZONE STANDARD
The U.S. Supreme Court rejected an attack on the Environmental Protection 
Agency's authority to write air quality standards, ruling Tuesday that 
Congress hadn't given the agency too much power to set pollution limits.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
02/27/eng-djn/eng-djn_140102_223_026655577123

MIRANT CORPORATION TO MOVE 1,000 MW IN POWER PACTS TO CALIFORNIA DEPARTMENT 
OF WATER RESOURCES
Mirant Corp. agreed to shift 1,000 megawatts in power contracts from the 
California Power Exchange to the Department of Water Resources, which is 
acting as the state's electricity buyer.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
02/27/eng-djn/eng-djn_210051_3_53283406700939

UTILICORP STILL ON MIDWEST ISO FENCE DESPITE LOOMING DEADLINE
Utilicorp United Inc. has not yet decided whether to officially become a 
member of the Midwest Independent Transmission System Operator Inc. grid 
operating group, a company executive said Tuesday.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
02/27/eng-djn/eng-djn_190100_193_388186472002

